        <li><strong>Campaign support</strong> — Landing pages and promotional features</li>
        <li><strong>UX oversight</strong> — User experience improvements across the purchase funnel</li>
        <li><strong>Team collaboration</strong> — Agile process with marketers, backend devs, and UX designers</li>
      </ul>

